title: #145:  Ain't Buying It With Eddie Bravo
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli. We welcome Eddie Bravo back to find out what he thinks about all the current events going on in the world and guess what? He ain't buying any of it. This episode is an instant classic.
Please check out my special "Zero Fucks" on Vimeo.com
It's available at Vimeo.com/ondemand/ZeroFucks
Come check Eddie Bravo and myself live at the Zanies in Chicago Dec 15th at 11pm.
http://zanieschicago.laughstub.com/event.cfm?id=518064
Thank you for your support!
